video.title: Small Time Gangster
video.synopsis: This Australian drama series follows the adventures of Tony Piccolo, a seemingly average joe who secretly works as an underworld enforcer.

episodes.synopsis: Leaving his unsuspecting family for an emergency "job," standover man Tony Piccolo is forced to collect from an old friend.
episodes.title: Jingle Bells

episodes.synopsis: Tony loses his nerve on a job, only to be saved by his new apprentice, the boss' son, while back home, Cathy bonds with their hunky neighbor.
episodes.title: The Yips

episodes.synopsis: Collecting from a lowlife client, Tony's nerves desert him again, leading to an unwise confession. Cathy's friendship with Brent takes a new turn.
episodes.title: Dangerous Talk

episodes.synopsis: Suspicious, Cathy follows Tony and finds him with Darlene. Trying to calm her, Tony confesses all, but she still thinks he's lying.
episodes.title: Who's Got the RPG?

episodes.synopsis: Trying to cope on her own, Cathy gets an unwelcome visitor.  Meanwhile, Tony employs an unusual tactic to extract payment from a client.
episodes.title: Suburban Beatdown

episodes.synopsis: When Tony wants out, Les decides to take matters into his own hands, despite the consequences. Meanwhile, Mel and Charlie rekindle their romance.
episodes.title: The Last Post

episodes.synopsis: Under pressure from Barry to deliver monies owed, Tony, Darlene and Steve accept a dangerous job. But can Darlene and Steve be trusted?
episodes.title: Stand And Deliver

episodes.synopsis: Tony receives bad news about Les from an unlikely source and decides to confront his demons once and for all. But nothing goes as planned.
episodes.title: Vengance
